property_one.title: The Last of the Mohicans
property_one.description: Good local food, great service, and a great place to hang out.  The place is a bit small, but the food is great.  The service is great, and the prices are reasonable.

property_two.title: Happy House
property_two.description: Great location and huge house. On the street, there is a lot of shopping and restaurants. The house is very clean and has a great view of the city.
